\c 137 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 137\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Boo'icha Warra Biyya Baabilonitti Booji'amanii
\m \bd 1\bd* Nuyi biyya Baabilonitti lagoota bishaanii bira teenyee, yommuu Xiyoonin yaadanne in boonye.
\m \bd 2\bd* Kiraarota keenya alaltuu achi jirutti fafannifne.
\m \bd 3\bd* Achitti immoo warri nu booji'an akka nuyi isaaniif weeddifnu, warri nu dhiphisanis gammachuudhaan akka isaaniif faarfannu nu irraa barbaadan; "Weedduu Xiyoon keessaas tokko nuuf weeddisaa!" jedhan.
\m \bd 4\bd* Wanta Waaqayyoof weeddifnu, attamitti biyya ormaatti weeddisuu dandeenya ree?
\m \bd 5\bd* Yaa Yerusaalem, ani yoon si irraanfadhe, harki koo mirgaa hojii isaa haa irraanfatu!
\m \bd 6\bd* Ani yoon si yaadachuu dhabaadhe, wanta ani itti gammadu hundumaa irra Yerusaalemin yoon caalchifachuu dhabaadhe, arrabni koo laagaa kootti haa gogu.
\m \bd 7\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, gaafa Yerusaalem diigamte, warri Edoom, "Diigaa, hamma hundee isheetiitti diigaa!" akka jedhan yaadadhu!
\m \bd 8\bd* Yaa mandara Baabilon, yaa barbadeessituu! Waan ati nu irratti hojjetteef, isa dugda siif baasu sanaaf haa tolu.
\m \bd 9\bd* Mucoolii kee qabee isa dhagaa irratti caccabsu sanaaf haa tolu!
\b 
